description.narrative: The project development objective is to improve sustainable management and use of the URT?s Exclusive Economic Zone, territorial seas, and coastal resources. Sustainable management and use will be reflected in enhanced revenue collection, reduced threats to the environment, improved livelihoods of participating coastal communities and improved institutional arrangements.

condition.narrative: Borrower shall ensure that annual work plans are prepared and submit to the Association for review
Borrower shall maintain the EGFT for such period as shall be agreed upon with the Association to facilitate implementation of theproject
Borrower shall prepare annual progress reports
Borrower shall prepare quarterly progress reports for each calendar quarter of each year of Project implementation
The Borrower shall maintain the Project Steering Committee for prpoviding overall policy guidance for the project.
The Borrower shall maintain the Technical Committee to provide technical advisory services for the project.
The project shall be implemented in accordance with the PIM, the Op. Manual of TASAF, MOU with TASAF, Disctrict MOUs.
